cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the classification of road users using radar sensors, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of classifier ensembles and feature selection is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The application of the method is towards autonomous driving (cs.RO) and the use of recurrent neural networks is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
